              "type": "text",
              "left": 80,
              "top": 412,
              "width": 840,
              "height": 76,
              "content": "<p style=\"font-size: 20px; text-align: center;\"><strong>想一想：</strong>1/2 块蛋糕和 3/4 瓶果汁，哪个更多？</p>",
